normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(82, 87, 99); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">成长型思维在商业、职场、人际关系、教育、艺术、体育等众多领域，都发挥着非常重要的作用。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(82, 87, 99); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(82, 87, 99); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在职场中，</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">具有成长型思维的企业和团队更具有包容性。</strong>具有成长型思维的领导更善于倾听他人的批判性建议，更重视员工的个人发展。而具有成长型思维的员工，在具有挑战性的任务中更有竞争力。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(82, 87, 99); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(82, 87, 99); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在人际关系中，具有成长型思维的人更具同理心，会主动经营关系，相信感情和关系是可以培养和发展的。</strong>社交场合，他们会更多地关心他人，而非聚焦于别人对自己可能的负面评价上，因此也更容易突破害羞等性格因素导致的社交障碍，积极地与他人互动。出现矛盾时，具有成长型思维的人更善于主动沟通和修复关系。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(82, 87, 99); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(82, 87, 99); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在教育领域，拥有成长型思维的孩子，看重结果也看重过程，更能享受到努力与成长的乐趣。</strong>他们更乐于寻求帮助，更为坚毅，心理更有弹性，复原力更强。具有成长型思维的父母，更善于称赞孩子的努力，教孩子拥抱挫折和挑战。具有成长型思维的老师，更乐于引导而不是评判学生。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(82, 87, 99); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(82, 87, 99); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;">此外，在体育竞技、艺术创造、创新创业等其他领域，成长型思维也发挥着重要的作用。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(82, 87, 99); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(82, 87, 99); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">成长型思维模式能够帮助你发现更多的机会，让你的未来拥有更多的可能。一旦形成成长型思维模式，你就获得了终身发展的优势。</span></p><p><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app4Kj7EZSY3675/image/ueditor/7009200_1550191521.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="700.jpg"/></p>

4.卓越领导者如何应对逆境？

