: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;">近年来，成长型思维正成为英美国家研究的新热点，甫一引进国内，立即引起很多人的共鸣。乔·欧文的《成长型思维：从平凡到优秀的七种思维模式》一书中所提到的观点，正受到越来越多读者的关注和欢迎。<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;">乔·欧文发现，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">杰出、成功的职场人士之所以和其他人不一样，其原因不仅仅在于他们的技能，更在于他们超越成功、终身成长的七种重要思维模式。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;">乔·欧文把成长型思维概括为<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">志存高远、勇于行动、坚韧不屈、积极乐观、承担责任、善于合作和不断成长</strong>七种思维模式，并为读者提供了一组简单易学、操作性强的工具，帮助人们开阔视野，优化思维，提高技能，做出更大的成就。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-