<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 145, 163); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">人是如何从平凡走向优秀乃至卓越的？</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0px; word-wrap: break-word !important;">为什么有些人多有建树，有些人却一事无成？杰出、成功的职场人士和普罗大众有什么不同？……</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 145, 163); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(87, 145, 163); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">技能、智商、环境……不同的人有不同的际遇自然有不同的答案。但乔·欧文在《成长型思维》一书中提出，思维模式的不同，可能是区分平凡和优秀的重要分水岭。如果说人的能力提升是“打怪技巧”的提升，那么培养成长型思维将帮助你“转型升级”。</span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; width: 300px; height: 90px; vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app4Kj7EZSY3675/image/ueditor/35384900_1550125877.cn/mmbiz_png/kw2nrmk65sftbg1w826gj09z62pghfzsqudbvnbkvaahr3crjdfvrbplgsrfx14dsmdd8muib6oqdklhjckequg/640?wx_fmt=png&#39;); background-attachment: scroll; background-size: contain; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(70, 87, 114); letter-spacing: 1px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">何谓成长型思维</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(82, 87, 99);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;">成长型思维是斯坦福大学行为心理学教授卡罗尔·徳韦克提出的一个概念。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;">德韦克指出，随着年龄的增长，人们逐渐建立起关于自已的思维模式。所谓思维模式，指的是决定一个人如何解释现实并做出反应的内心态度。卡罗尔·徳韦克将人的思维模式区分为<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“固定型思维”</strong>和<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“成长型思维”</strong>，不同的思维模式影响着一个人的行为选择，并最终决定一个人会活出什么样的人生。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 676.997px; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 640.017px; box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) 3.53553px 3.53553px 8px; display: inline-block; border-color: white; height: auto !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app4Kj7EZSY3675/image/ueditor/35906500_1550125877.cn/mmbiz_png/kw2nrmk65sftbg1w826gj09z62pghfzsb42spas91egnrp29rianh2ytkoifdru7hhxeqia65ewbwhfho8gdqiahw/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; height: auto !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 640px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(82, 87, 99);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">在固定型思维模式之下，一个人常常认为事物是一成不变的。他们总是静态地、片面地去看待一个人或一件事，更习惯于去寻找消极的因素，对世界的认识也总是偏于消极。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">固定思维模式下的人不相信人会改变，在面对别人的缺点与不足时，更多的是打击与否定。他们惧怕犯错，不愿接受挑战，认为人的能力与生俱来，&nbsp;即使努力也不会有大的提高。<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">在成长型思维模式之下，一个人看待世界的方式倾向乐观，看重成长，往往相信人的各种基本素质都可以通过自身的努力得到改善，长期的训练和努力可以发掘一个人内在的潜能。<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;">成长型思维的人认为挑战可以帮助人们学习和成长，挑战失败意味着“我还有成长的空间”，坚信努力是取得进步的必由之路，挑战和失败可以暴露出自己的不足，而弥补这些不足就是下一个努力的目标。他们对能够增强自身能力的反馈信息更关注，他们欢迎批评性意见，尽力改进自己的行为，他们欣赏他人的成功，并注意从中学习经验，获得激励和成长。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 676.997px; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 640.017px; box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) 3.53553px 3.53553px 8px; display: inline-block; border-color: white; height: auto !important;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app4Kj7EZSY3675/image/ueditor/49576700_1550125877.cn/mmbiz_png/kw2nrmk65sftbg1w826gj09z62pghfzswicgejjvpsnibci3tmuywc9xkmczhhqalteqylvgrzeqgw5yib5b05ksg/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(238, 237, 235); vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(238, 237, 235); background-size: 22px; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; height: auto !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 640px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(82, 87, 99);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;">研究表明，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">绝大部分人都兼具两种思维模式。</span>一个人在不同的阶段、不同领域可能会有不同的思维模式。只是，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果固定型思维模式一旦形成且占据主导，除非有意识地觉察和改变，很可能会让一个人的发展极其受限。</strong><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;">对于机构、组织、企业而言，占据主导的组织文化是固定型思维还是成长型思维，对其发展的影响也不可小觑。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(82, 87, 99);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; width: 300px; height: 90px; vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app4Kj7EZSY3675/image/ueditor/35384900_1550125877.cn/mmbiz_png/kw2nrmk65sftbg1w826gj09z62pghfzsqudbvnbkvaahr3crjdfvrbplgsrfx14dsmdd8muib6oqdklhjckequg/640?wx_fmt=png&#39;); background-attachment: scroll; background-size: contai